---
import V3InteriorLayout from '../../../layouts/V3InteriorLayout.astro';
---

<V3InteriorLayout
  title="Amazon Basin - A Sunset Journey Home"
  eyebrow="Set story"
  description="Maya Fourteen's sunset session recorded live in the Amazon Basin, Mato Grosso, Brazil: organic tech, tribal textures and progressive vibes where the world's largest rainforest begins."
>
  <div class="video-frame">
    <iframe
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IRV1sNs9aTk"
      title="Live DJ Set at Amazon Basin (Sunset Session), Mato Grosso, Brazil | Maya Fourteen"
      loading="lazy"
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
      allowfullscreen
    ></iframe>
  </div>

  <p>
    This is the homecoming. A sunset session recorded live in the heart of the Amazon Basin, in
    Mato Grosso, the homeland, where the rivers and lagoons begin to converge and nature dances
    to its own rhythm. The set was designed to honor that: a selection inspired by the lush
    landscape and the soulful energy of the region.
  </p>
  <p>
    It moves through organic tech, tribal textures and progressive vibes as the sun dips below
    the world's largest rainforest. This is the long burn in its purest form: organic
    percussion, emotional storytelling, a rhythm that breathes with the landscape.
  </p>

  <h2>The journey</h2>
  <ul class="tracklist">
    <li>Pablo Fierro, Hyenah - Panoramica</li>
    <li>Ameme - Your Vibe</li>
    <li>The Angels feat. Idd Aziz - Jungle Walk</li>
    <li>Boy Oh Boy - Ko Kora</li>
    <li>Eran Hersh - Yums</li>
    <li>Dave S. - Everything Comes In Threes</li>
    <li>Matthias Meyer, Budakid - Hybrid Society</li>
    <li>Sam Davies - Cosmos</li>
    <li>Stan Kolev - Inward</li>
    <li>Kintar, Delum - Sophie</li>
    <li>Swedish House Mafia, The Weeknd - Moth To A Flame</li>
  </ul>

  <a class="cta-button" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IRV1sNs9aTk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Watch the full set on YouTube</a>
</V3InteriorLayout>

<style>
  .video-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .video-frame iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  p {
    text-align: justify;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-size: 1.35em;
    margin: 1.6em 0 0.5em;
  }

  .tracklist {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: 0.88em;
    line-height: 1.9;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    p {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
